---
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro"
import mobileImg from "../assets/images/image-web-3-mobile.jpg"
---

<haeader >
    <Image src={mobileImg} alt="HeroImage" class="mb-8"/>

    <h1 class="text-[2.5rem]/10 font-extrabold">The Bright Future of Web 3.0?</h1>

    <p class="text-Dark-grayish-blue text-[.9374rem] mb-6">We dive into the next evolution of the web that claims to put the power of the platforms back into the hands of the people. 
    But is it really fulfilling its promise?</p>

    <button class="bg-Soft-red uppercase px-8 py-3 font-bold cursor-pointer hover:bg-Soft-red/90 text-Off-white">Read more</button>
</haeader>